stead.com/files/hm9.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> /shrug<br><br>You just give him the ring (stay in range) then run! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualtubren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Altubren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/17/02 5:27:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> You can do that while being attacked?  Should I try wolf form with him? <p><HTML><BODY><a Target="_top" href="http://www.flamingtext.com/ezb.html" ><img src="http://ezb.flamingtext.com/ezb/2002/06/16/flamingtext_com_1024282346_31089.jpg"></BODY></HTML><br>52 Wanderer of Tunare's Court<br>A druid's job is never done...</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unotus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Notus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/_ht_a/Cyrion7/celtic/animated/spiral01.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Druid of the Southwind</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/18/02 9:26:45 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> Not sure what the issue was.  Perhaps:<br><br>1.  Have you assisted (multiple) other Druids/Rangers in their epic fights, especially against the DE Corruptor in Karanas?<br><br>2.  Do you (by actions past) have a very low faction with him otherwise?<br><br><br>I couldnt get him to stop (ages ago) when I turned in my ring.  I merely ran to keep up with him, popped the ring in the window, and hit trade.  He accepted, gave the dialogue, &quot;flipped&quot; the worn (?) coin back to me and his buddy spawned.<br><br>I smiled and sauntered to the zone to lose aggro.<br><br>Notus SulVento<br>Hierophant of Clan Phoenix<br>Xegony <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualtubren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Altubren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/19/02 6:42:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> Seems as though it is an aggro issue.  As a wood elf I get attacked once I come into range.  I am not sure if being wood elf makes my faction low to begin with, but neither have I assisted in killing a DE of any kind as my druid.  I did come back again (seems if he is aggroed he despawns when you zone and pops 8 hours later) in wolf form, ran up to him presented the ring to him, and he gave me the coin.  WOOT!, no it is off to Telin and then to whack a DE Corruptor and some Reavers while saving some Rangers in East Karana!!! <p><HTML><BODY><a Target="_top" href="http://www.flamingtext.com/ezb.html" ><img src="http://ezb.flamingtext.com/ezb/2002/06/16/flamingtext_com_1024282346_31089.jpg"border=0 alt="Image by FlamingText.com"></a></BODY></HTML><br>52 Wanderer of Tunare's Court<br>A druid's job is never done...</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unotus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Notus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/_ht_a/Cyrion7/celtic/animated/spiral01.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Druid of the Southwind</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/19/02 6:23:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> Still not sure what it may have been.  I'm a Wood Elf, and had no aggro issue with him (no illusion on) when I handed mine in until the Reaver spawned.<br><br>This was a looong time ago, so any patch/nerf/enhancement in all that time may have affected his views on faction.<br><br>In any event, congrats on your coin, and best wishes on the completion of your epic. <p><div align="center"><b><a href =mailto:sulvento@hotmail.com>Notus SulVento</a><br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=38079>Hierophant</a><a href=http://www.clanphoenix.org> of  Clan Phoenix</a><br></b><b></div></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualtubren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Altubren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/20/02 9:30:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> Thank you Notus!!!<br><br>Now I am seriously hung on the tainted/corrupt Aqua Goblin Shaman.  11 hours and counting and no spawn...&lt;sigh&gt; Tedious.  Not to mention the fact that the deepwaters almost roast my Woody Butt in the process!!! <p><HTML><BODY><a Target="_top" href="http://www.flamingtext.com/ezb.html" ><img src="http://ezb.flamingtext.com/ezb/2002/06/16/flamingtext_com_1024282346_31089.jpg"border=0 alt="Image by FlamingText.com"></a></BODY></HTML><br>52 Wanderer of Tunare's Court<br>A druid's job is never done...</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uhennethak.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hennethak</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/20/02 12:25:33 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> The shaman sucks to get spawned, so will the gorilla and the barracuda. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualtubren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Altubren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/20/02 1:12:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> Can't argue there, but can he spawn in any of the spots at the tower or just the three spawns near Deep?  I have been pulling the Deepwaters around Deep and the really put a SERIOUS burn on my hide.  I can pretty much melee solo the aqua goblins and the normal shamen.  Just very new to this, and the guide is only so much help. <p><HTML><BODY><a Target="_top" href="http://www.flamingtext.com/ezb.html" ><img src="http://ezb.flamingtext.com/ezb/2002/06/16/flamingtext_com_1024282346_31089.jpg"border=0 alt="Image by FlamingText.com"></a></BODY></HTML><br>52 Wanderer of Tunare's Court<br>A druid's job is never done...</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugreggorumbletum.showPublicProfile?language=EN>greggo rumbletum</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/20/02 2:42:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> Just the 2 on the &quot;outside&quot; of the three spawn by Deep.  THe middle guy is for the cleric epic (this but CAN be MQed by the way so if you have the mana pull all three and do a cleric somewhere a favour <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualtubren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Altubren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/20/02 3:45:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> THAT! is VERY useful information!!! Thanks a TON! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><HTML><BODY><a Target="_top" href="http://www.flamingtext.com/ezb.html" ><img src="http://ezb.flamingtext.com/ezb/2002/06/16/flamingtext_com_1024282346_31089.jpg"border=0 alt="Image by FlamingText.com"></a></BODY></HTML><br>52 Wanderer of Tunare's Court<br>A druid's job is never done...</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unotus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Notus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/_ht_a/Cyrion7/celtic/animated/spiral01.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Druid of the Southwind</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/20/02 9:55:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A bit of advice if possible please...</span><hr size=1> Dig around for the epic threads...there is lots of advice stored away that will make your journey a tad easier. <p><div align="center"><b><a href =mailto:sulvento@hotmail.com>Notus SulVento</a><br><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=38079>Hierophant</a><a href=http://www.clanphoenix.org> of  Clan Phoenix</a><br></b><b></div></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showPrevMessage?topicID=5358.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showNextMessage?topicID=5358.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5358.topic&index=11><img src=http://www.execpc.com/~msippel/thedruidsgrove/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.emailToFriend?topicID=5358.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovequests.threadControl?topicID=5358.topic><im